com.contentful.java.cma.model

Class CMAWebhook

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.contentful.java.cma.model.CMAResource
      • com.contentful.java.cma.model.CMAWebhook

  • public class CMAWebhook
extends CMAResource
    Represents one webhook definition.

    A valid webhook needs to at least have called setName(String), setUrl(String), addTopic(CMAWebhookTopic).
